<li id="area1"><img src="http://static.8264.com/oldcms/moban/zt/material2013/img/image001.jpg" class="pic220">
<p>Maggie Niu<br>
CORDURA&reg;品牌亚太区市场经理<br>
Maggie在时尚和户外相关行业拥有超过15年市场营销方面的工作经验。在加入英威达CORDURA&reg;品牌团队之前，她曾负责过Levi&rsquo;s&reg;、The North Face&reg;中国的营销策略和品牌管理活动，包括媒体广告、公关活动、店铺设计、渠道营销和视觉陈列。<br>
作为CORDURA&reg; 品牌亚太区市场经理，Maggie负责制定品牌在亚太区的市场拓展营销策略和业务模式的建立，推行旨在提高CORDURA&reg;品牌在亚太地区市场份额和消费者认知度的广告和促销活动。<br>
Maggie毕业于东华大学，拥有服装设计与工程学士学位和服装市场营销管理硕士学位。 </p>
<p>Maggie Niu <br>
AP CORDURA&reg; Brand End-Use Marketing Manager<br>
Niu brings more than 15 years&rsquo; experience in fashion and outdoor related industries, specialized in marketing. Prior to joining INVISTA&rsquo;S CORDURA&reg; brand team, she used to serve for Levi&rsquo;s&reg;, The North Face&reg;, where she developed marketing strategies and managed effective brand and trade marketing activities in China including advertising, public relations, store design, trade marketing and visual merchandising.<br>
In her role as AP end-use marketing manager, Niu develops and executes pull-through marketing strategies, business models, and complimentary advertising and promotional campaigns designed to increase trade and consumer awareness for the CORDURA&reg; brand in the Asia Pacific region.<br>
Niu earned a Bachelor&rsquo;s Degree in fashion design and apparel engineering as well as a Master&rsquo;s Degree in fashion marketing at Donghua University.</p>
</li>
