<li id="area4"><img src="http://static.8264.com/oldcms/moban/zt/material2013/img/image004.png" class="pic220">
<p>Craig Knight<br>
运徽国际销售副总裁<br>
Craig Knight 作为公司创始人之一，担任WINHIGH全球销售及市场营销副总裁,负责带领着海外团队制定WINHIGH全球业务策略及市场和品牌推广<br>
Craig具有在不同行业领域内从事全球市场营销和业务管理超过20年的经验。在其任职于全球大型跨国公司的15年时间里，Craig带领国际团队取得过很多骄人战绩<br>
Craig定居澳大利亚悉尼，并在新加坡及中国居住过7年。他本人十分推崇积极健康的户外生活方式，乐于尝试各种户外运动尤其热衷冲浪，滑雪及航行。<br> Craig先生拥有澳洲悉尼大学理学学士学位以及澳大利亚管理研究生院工商管理学硕士学位，具有非常专业的学术背景。</p>
<p>Craig Knight<br>
Vice President of Winhigh<br>
Craig Knight is Vice-President of International Sales & Marketing for Winhigh, and a founder of the company. He leads the development and implementation of Winhigh global business strategy and brand promotion. 
With a diverse industrial background, Craig has 20 years extensive working experience in International Sales & Marketing and Business Management roles. He has launched several successful businesses after 15 years working in large multinationals.
<br>
Craig resides in Sydney, Australia and lived for seven years in Singapore and China. He promotes sustainability and a healthy outdoor lifestyle, enjoying surfing, snowboarding, sailing, and the great outdoors. <br>
Craig holds a Bachelor of Science degree from the University of Sydney (Australia) and a Masters of Business Administration from the Australian Graduate School of Management.</p>
</li>
<li id="area5"><img src="http://static.8264.com/oldcms/moban/zt/material2013/img/image005.jpg" class="pic220">
<p>丁雪梅<br>
香港理工大学博士、英国宝洁技术中心博士后、东华大学教授、博士生导师<br>
丁雪梅曾就职于Liz Claiborne Ltd. Co.、Zellweger Uster Co.等著名纺织服装外资公司以及上海市服装研究所等单位。2003年作为"优秀海外留学回国人员"引进东华大学，2008年起担任香港纺织生物工程及信息学会董事，2009年入选上海市浦江人才计划。研究领域包括1）国际纺织品服装市场准入要求；2）织物护理技术；3）纺织服装材料功能与舒适性等。2004年以来主持或主要参与科技部、国家自然科学基金、教育部、上海市科委科研项目等科研项目近20项，同时接受美国宝洁公司、博西华（德国）电器有限公司、香港制衣业训练局资助开展项目合作。发表论文150余篇，出版著作3部；省部级科研获奖3项。<br>
<br>
</p>
<p>Dr. Ding Xuemei<br>
Dr. Xuemei Ding is the professor and doctoral supervisor in the department of apparel design and engineering at Donghua University.<br>
from Northwest Institute of Textile Science and Technology, and gained her Ph. D. in Apparel Materials from The Hong Kong Polytechnic University in 2003. She ever worked with Liz Claiborne International Limited Shanghai office, Shanghai Garment Group Co. Technical R&D Center, Zellweger Uster (Shanghai) Co. Ltd. as well as Procter & Gamber Newcastle Technical Center, UK respectively. Dr. Ding has conducted numerous research projects covering technical requirements for international textile and apparel trade, safety, hygiene and environmental protection of textiles and apparel, technology for fabric care, heat and moisture transfer in textile materials and apparel and so on. She has published more than 150 peer-reviewed and conference papers. <br>
<br>
</p>
</li>
<li id="area8"><img src="http://static.8264.com/oldcms/moban/zt/material2013/img/image008.jpg" class="pic220">
<p>朱林<br>
功能性纤维中国区销售总监<br>
与1995年毕业于上海大学机械工程专业和科技外事专业，双学士学位。并于当年加入杜邦公司，任莱卡&reg;纤维生产工程师。1998年起任杜邦公司华东区技术市场主管，负责向莱卡&reg;纤维的客户提供技术服务。2002年起任亚太区莱卡&reg;纤维客户使用端负责人，主要负责调节客户生产工艺，找出最佳工艺设定。2004年在杜邦纺织公司转为英威达公司之后，任功能性纤维中国区销售总监，同时负责功能性产品相关联的技术服务。相关功能性品牌有 COOLMAX&reg; 面料,THERMOLITE&reg;面料， LYCRA&reg;T400&reg; 纤维等。
</p>
<p>Duncan Zhu</p>
<p>Branded Specialty Sales Director, China</p>
<p>Duncan zhu has more than 18years’ experience in textile industries, specialized in fiber end-use support  and the branded-fiber sales part. He holds a double bachelors of mechanical engineering & technical export service. He joined the Dupont TM as the LYCRA&reg; fiber manufacture- engineer . From 1998 to  2002, he serviced the LYCRA&reg; fiber customers of the east china as the technical & market manager. From 2002 to 2004 , he work as the AP-VIU(value in use) director ,who support the customers in the optimal design about the detail textile process. <br>
 In his new role of the China branded specialty sales director of INVISTA, he develop a Sales strategy (Products, Price, Channel) for fibers, and develop intimate knowledge of the market, values and requirements to serve(as COOLMAX&reg; fabric , THERMOLITE&reg; fabric ,LYCRA&reg;T400&reg; fiber etc…).  </p>
</li>
<li id="area6"><img src="http://static.8264.com/oldcms/moban/zt/material2013/img/image006.png" class="pic220">
<p>梁方民<br>
高士<br>
梁方民先生来自高士――全球最大工业缝纫线制造及供应商，总部位于英国伦敦。梁先生负责带领高士中国技术销售团队为制衣厂，品牌及买家提供有关工业缝纫线选择与应用的专业技术知识以求帮助其客户在使用高士产品过程中获取最大得益。同时，得益于将近十六年的缝纫线生产与新产品研发经验，梁先生积极参与新产品，新服务开发与推广工作以满足日新月异的中国服装市场的需要。<br>
梁先生就读于华南理工大学化学工程系。1996年毕业后，其加入高士服务至今。从事于品管，研发，生产及销售等不同管理与技术工作岗位。<br>
</p>
<p>Fangmin Liang (F.M. Liang) Coats Head of Technical Sales, Coats China F.M. Liang is from Coats C the world's largest industrial sewing thread manufacturers and suppliers, headquartered in London, United Kingdom.  Mr. Liang leads Coats China Technical Sales team responsible for providing technical advice in the context of industrial sewing thread selection and application to garment factory, Brand and Buyer so as to assist Coats client to gain best value from the products they use.  With almost 16 years of service in sewing thread production and R&D areas, F.M. is actively engaged in new product & service development and roll-out to cater for the needs of apparel market that is changing at a rapid pace in China.<br>
Mr. Liang started his career in Coats in 1996 after he graduated from South China University of Technology with a BS degree in Chemical Engineering.  He had served in different management and technical positions for the areas of QA, R&D, Production and Sales over its 16-year service in Coats.</p>
</li>
